<div id="review_1437624186" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1437624186" />
    <a title="Debra Johnson" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/24401416-debra-johnson"><img alt="Debra Johnson" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1552412007p2/24401416.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1437624186?book_show_action=true">Feb 12, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Debra Johnson" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Debra Johnson" href="/user/show/24401416-debra-johnson">Debra Johnson</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/24401416-debra-johnson?shelf=erotica">erotica</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/24401416-debra-johnson?shelf=shared-2-bookbub">shared-2-bookbub</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/24401416-debra-johnson?shelf=kindle-lendable">kindle-lendable</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/24401416-debra-johnson?shelf=shared-2-google">shared-2-google</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/24401416-debra-johnson?shelf=romance">romance</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/24401416-debra-johnson?shelf=1-owned-all">1-owned-all</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/24401416-debra-johnson?shelf=shared-2-facebook">shared-2-facebook</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/24401416-debra-johnson?shelf=contemporary">contemporary</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/24401416-debra-johnson?shelf=prch-amz-verified">prch-amz-verified</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/24401416-debra-johnson?shelf=adult">adult</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1437624186" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12143634257430096548"><a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/24381738.Abuse__Abuse___1_' title='Abuse (Abuse, #1) by Nikki Sex' rel='nofollow noopener'>Abuse</a> by <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/6585579.Nikki_Sex' title='Nikki Sex' rel='nofollow noopener'>Nikki Sex</a><br/>Genres: Adult, Contemporary, Erotica, Romance, and a new category for me, Psychology/Mental Illness<br/>?????Stars I have no clue what to rate this. I will decide.....Eventually!<br/>*******************************************************<br/>4 stars<br/><br/>This book is broken down into 3 parts.<br/><br/>The 1st part is about &apos;The Monster&apos;, Grant, the male MC.<br/>This part I loved. You really get into Grant&apos;s head and he really digs his way into your heart.<br/><br/>The 2nd part is about Renata &apos;The Mouse&apos;, our female MC.<br/>Wh</span>
  <span id="freeText12143634257430096548" style="display:none"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/24381738.Abuse__Abuse___1_" title="Abuse (Abuse, #1) by Nikki Sex" rel="nofollow noopener">Abuse</a> by <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/6585579.Nikki_Sex" title="Nikki Sex" rel="nofollow noopener">Nikki Sex</a><br />Genres: Adult, Contemporary, Erotica, Romance, and a new category for me, Psychology/Mental Illness<br />?????Stars I have no clue what to rate this. I will decide.....Eventually!<br />*******************************************************<br />4 stars<br /><br />This book is broken down into 3 parts.<br /><br />The 1st part is about 'The Monster', Grant, the male MC.<br />This part I loved. You really get into Grant's head and he really digs his way into your heart.<br /><br />The 2nd part is about Renata 'The Mouse', our female MC.<br />While I loved most of this, the last few chapters in her part have repetition &amp; I abhor repetition. Her story will also get to you. The last few chapters though cost this story a partial star due to my abhorrence of the repetition I mentioned above. It slows everything down. <br /><br />Up to that point the flow was great &amp; moved beautifully.<br /><br />The 3rd part is about both Renata &amp; Grant. Their interaction with each other. <br />While I loved most of it, there is a lot more repetition and I did NOT like the way it ended. It felt ........ Contrived. Rushed. Awkward. I felt like there should have been another chapter and the whole conversation had an 'Unfinished' or 'Unrefined' quality to it.<br /><br />The repetition and this last scene is what caused the most loss of stars. <br /><br />This story is very 'Mentally' &amp; emotionally weighty. It is compelling to say the least. While I would recommend it to my friends who love adult romance, I would be very careful to watch for triggers. There are a lot of them in this story.<br /><br />Do not go into reading this book lightly!<br /><br />I recommend you have a light, funny, fluffy story ready to read for when you are done with this. You will be 'Perplexed' (to steal a GR friends word), 'Disconcerted' and even 'Bewildered'.<br />This story is 'VERY' complex. Psychologically Mind Bending. <br /><br />It is definitely an adult read with intimate scenes. The subject matter and the triggers that this story deals with should not be in the hands of the immature. I will not put an age on that. <br /><br />This ends on a cliffhanger &amp; I forgot about that before I started reading it. I HATE CLIFFHANGERS!<br /><br />I was going to wait a long time before I started reading the 2nd book in this 'Trilogy', but now that my brain has reset itself I have changed my mind. I will continue it in the near future.<br /><br />Don't say you haven't been warned. This book will Scramble your Brain.</span>
  <a data-text-id="12143634257430096548" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


