  <span id="freeText4879844321234047873" style="display:none">3.5 stars....<br />I'm in awe at the research and facts provided in this book about the horrors of different types of abuse and neglect. There was so much to learn about others who have been abused.<br />The story itself was just not my favorite but rather than leave a bad review I honestly think I was totally off on what I thought this would be like therefore my expectations ruined it for me.<br />I love to see anyone damaged and hurt overcome and learn to love.<br />It was fascinating to get to know the tortured souls of Grant and Renata.</span>
