<div id="review_1160918871" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1160918871" />
    <a title="Olga therebelreader" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/24443337-olga-therebelreader"><img alt="Olga therebelreader" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1540920390p2/24443337.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1160918871?book_show_action=true">Jan 08, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Olga therebelreader" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Olga therebelreader" href="/user/show/24443337-olga-therebelreader">Olga therebelreader</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/24443337-olga-therebelreader?shelf=highly-emotional">highly-emotional</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/24443337-olga-therebelreader?shelf=erotica-xxx">erotica-xxx</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/24443337-olga-therebelreader?shelf=suspense-angst">suspense-angst</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/24443337-olga-therebelreader?shelf=contemporary-romance">contemporary-romance</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/24443337-olga-therebelreader?shelf=romance">romance</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1160918871" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14797309947001357237">It&apos;s been a very interesting, mind blown journey for sure!!! The two main characters, Grant and Renata, were so well analyzed, that I instantly felt the connection. Abuse in any form it&apos;s expressed, physical, mental, sexual, emotional, verbal was the common focal point between Grant and Renata. They came to learn, with Andre&apos;s assistance, how to pass over their insecurities and fears from childhood abuse and discover together love and happiness. I didn&apos;t expect a cliffhanger when I started it, a</span>
  <span id="freeText14797309947001357237" style="display:none">It's been a very interesting, mind blown journey for sure!!! The two main characters, Grant and Renata, were so well analyzed, that I instantly felt the connection. Abuse in any form it's expressed, physical, mental, sexual, emotional, verbal was the common focal point between Grant and Renata. They came to learn, with Andre's assistance, how to pass over their insecurities and fears from childhood abuse and discover together love and happiness. I didn't expect a cliffhanger when I started it, and now I can't wait for the next installment. That was also my first acquaintance with sexual therapist Andre, whom I truly loved as a matchmaker. The only thing that I didn't enjoy was the erotic relationship between Andre and fragile Renata.</span>
