<span id="freeTextContainer587944584733339644">This read was intense!<br/><br/>Before I read this I had to get in the mood (psych myself up) because I knew it was going to appeal to all my senses as a book reader. I was right!<br/><br/>The author is incredible! As I always say it takes a truly unique story to knock a bookworm out of their own world and straight into another. <br/><br/>I truly hope the author has more in store for us!</span>

