        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1237161422" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13427001242493032623"><b> ☆☆☆☆☆5 Souls of Brokenness Stars☆☆☆☆☆</b><br/><br/> This book is heart twisting awesomeness. I can honestly say this is a hard review to put into the proper words it deserves. <br/><br/><a href='http://s945.photobucket.com/user/jamielk32/media/Mobile%20Uploads/PicsArt_1428888870735_zpszoctkxtk.jpg.html' target='_blank' rel='nofollow noopener'>
  <img src='https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1428916178i/14498668._SX540_.jpg' alt=' photo PicsArt_1428888870735_zpszoctkxtk.jpg' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/>
</a><br/><br/>The wordy , quirky, patient, amazing Dr Andre Chevalier gathers the broken pieces of hidden souls into his world to put back together. His ways are slow and kind with patience and thoughtfulness. The words he speaks are so enlightening, as a reader, this book crosses over into your life. <br/><br/><b> &quot;Many times karma comes from inside - with </b></span>
  <span id="freeText13427001242493032623" style="display:none"><b> ☆☆☆☆☆5 Souls of Brokenness Stars☆☆☆☆☆</b><br><br> This book is heart twisting awesomeness. I can honestly say this is a hard review to put into the proper words it deserves. <br><br><a href="http://s945.photobucket.com/user/jamielk32/media/Mobile%20Uploads/PicsArt_1428888870735_zpszoctkxtk.jpg.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">
  <img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1428916178i/14498668._SX540_.jpg" alt=" photo PicsArt_1428888870735_zpszoctkxtk.jpg" class="gr-hostedUserImg">
</a><br><br>The wordy , quirky, patient, amazing Dr Andre Chevalier gathers the broken pieces of hidden souls into his world to put back together. His ways are slow and kind with patience and thoughtfulness. The words he speaks are so enlightening, as a reader, this book crosses over into your life. <br><br><b> "Many times karma comes from inside - with each individual creating their own Heaven or Hell."</b><br><br><a href="http://s945.photobucket.com/user/jamielk32/media/Mobile%20Uploads/PicsArt_1428887869069_zpscnbgykne.jpg.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">
  <img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1428916178i/14498669._SY540_.jpg" alt=" photo PicsArt_1428887869069_zpscnbgykne.jpg" class="gr-hostedUserImg">
</a><br><br>Both Renata and Grant are pieced back together with the help of Andre. <br><br>Renata's broken puzzle pieces stem from a horrible and abusive father. Falling into the care of Andre as a young 18 year old, she learned to live thru loving a gift from Andre. She was pieced together thru small steps of loving something that needed her. As Andre continues with Renata's puzzle, she becomes a helping hand to other's with problems that also mend her own demons within. <br><br>Grant's puzzle was shattered at a very young age by the one person who was his hero....his father. The horrendous events of his childhood continue leading to other horrible events. These are revieled in small doses to us readers and still by the end of the book secrets aren't totally exposed. Andre teaches Grant he is not a monster. As Grant begins to heal, Andre leads Grant to Renata for the next puzzle piece to be placed.<br><br>Grant and Renata are beautiful together. Broken and hidden souls seeing the light together. Both needing to feel needed.<br><br><a href="http://s945.photobucket.com/user/jamielk32/media/Mobile%20Uploads/PicsArt_1428890224422_zpsgvpnfdqg.jpg.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">
  <img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1428916178i/14498670.jpg" alt=" photo PicsArt_1428890224422_zpsgvpnfdqg.jpg" class="gr-hostedUserImg">
</a><br><br><b> "The sun is shing. It's a beautiful day. All shadows have been banished. There's not a cloud in our hearts, or in the sky. This wonderful woman makes me feel so glad to be alive."</b><br><br>Then the phone rings......hell is about to darken their clear skies.<br><br>Damn, damn, damn.......this leads to book 2......I NEED IT NOW!</span>
